{"tid":1286274,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"《缺》MV 致每位保衛香港的人","createTime":"2019-07-04T22:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T23:25:18.000Z","uid":1181,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ebae26392b743ea7c29809787d4cd6c464d15271","tid":1286274,"uid":1181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T22:57:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n92H-renp5Y&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dn92H-renp5Y%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=J%2B7a%2FypYnyyex2M81OHxVWipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=a9e6d0ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n92H-renp5Y&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n感謝一眾手足連日黎既付出，所以整咗個mv同所有保衛香港既人講句多謝<br />\n無論面前有幾多困難，我地都唔會放棄任何人，一齊嬴一齊走<br />\n正如鄺仔話齋，唔好再有兄弟有事，希望呢首歌可以為大家帶黎力量，香港人係唔會咁易屈服！<br />\n就算前路有幾難，我地都要繼續，<strong>一。齊。行。落。去</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港人的五大訴求<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n《缺》 張敬軒 <br />\n作詞：陳耀森<br />\n作曲：徐沛昕<br />\n編曲：Mac Chew<br />\n監製：張敬軒<br />\n<br />\n當天這道門合上<br />\n冰箱裏沒人在雪中送炭 呼吸缺氧<br />\n這一帶並無路向<br />\n漆黑裏為燃亮我的信仰 歷遍風霜<br />\n冰封了血肉無能力擋一仗<br />\n活像無名氏為愛戰死沙場<br />\n你沒贈我急救藥箱<br />\n<br />\n今天你避談實相<br />\n修葺那牧場飼養白綿羊 生活如常<br />\n即使我滯留門內竭力拍響 不變你睡相<br />\n談維持現狀安好 遠遠説不上<br />\n氣候過時何以遏止我 尋方向<br />\n<br />\n殘破身軀注滿熱血<br />\n堅拒眼前由誰掠奪 日後歲月<br />\n以初心 對抗暴雪<br />\n不怕在低溫中氣喘 願望無懼否決<br />\n理想長存 高空盤旋 從不缺<br />\n這困局 就用雙手 來解脫<br />\n<br />\n今天你為求獲勝<br />\n鋪天蓋地營造了偽和平 虛幻無形<br />\n封鎖我路途然後隔絕救兵 恐怕我做反應<br />\n如何憑極地飛霜 凍結我本性<br />\n我亦會重燃我這一套 求生本領<br />\n<br />\n殘破身軀注滿熱血<br />\n堅拒眼前由誰掠奪 日後歲月<br />\n以初心 對抗暴雪<br />\n不怕在低溫中氣喘 願望無懼否決<br />\n理想長存 高空盤旋 從不缺<br />\n心裡夢 熱度總可 融解積雪<br />\n<br />\n縱沒閒情逸致換快樂<br />\n面前 問題才是冰山一角<br />\n藏著我 埋沒我 仍有知覺<br />\n<br />\n這身軀注滿熱血<br />\n堅拒眼前由誰掠奪 日後歲月<br />\n冷風吹 對鏡自説<br />\n終有樂土可給眷戀 仍然可望見樂園<br />\n求存意志力與部署 從不缺<br />\n於困局 就用雙手 來解脫<br />\n這困局 就用雙手 對決<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n影片素材來源：<br />\n看中國：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wRpGM...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwRpGM...&d=J%2B7a%2FypYnyyex2M81OHxVWipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=49a48fa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wRpGM...</a><br />\nRFA 自由亞洲粵語：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TsEbb...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTsEbb...&d=J%2B7a%2FypYnyyex2M81OHxVWipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=14974128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TsEbb...</a><br />\nVIU TV 經緯線<br />\njoechan：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_tqIX...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_tqIX...&d=J%2B7a%2FypYnyyex2M81OHxVWipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=55c1ef8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_tqIX...</a><br />\n報導者 The Reporter：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yuwRt...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyuwRt...&d=J%2B7a%2FypYnyyex2M81OHxVWipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=a8125152\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yuwRt...</a><br />\nhkbeliever：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zRrQR...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzRrQR...&d=J%2B7a%2FypYnyyex2M81OHxVWipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=84836535\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zRrQR...</a><br />\n鏗鏘集：讓聲音聽得見：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zDP6F...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzDP6F...&d=J%2B7a%2FypYnyyex2M81OHxVWipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=70deeda6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zDP6F...</a><br />\nFTVV：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v4-kL...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dv4-kL...&d=J%2B7a%2FypY